    "/posts/": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "posts (貼文)"
        ],
        "description": "  <p>取得所有貼文。</p>  參數用法：  <ul>  <li><code>timeSort</code> 參數：  <ol>  <li>預設新到舊</li>  <li>是否有 <code>'asc'</code> 值？，有值有舊到新；沒值有新到舊。</li>  </ol>  </li>  <li><code>q</code> 參數：  <ol>  <li>查找物件中的留言 <code>discussContent</code>。</li>  <li>用正則表達式以 JS 轉 mongDB 語法 <code>.find( parName: /<查尋字串>/)</code>。</li>  </ol>  </li>  <li>取得 Token 至上方 Authorize 按鈕以格式 <code>Bearer ＜Token＞</code> 加入設定，swagger 文件中鎖頭上鎖表示登入，可使用登入權限。</li>  </ul>  ",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "timeSort",
            "in": "query",
            "type": "string"
          },
          {
            "name": "q",
            "in": "query",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "  取得全部貼文  ",
            "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "status": {
                  "type": "boolean",
                  "example": true
                },
                "data": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "_id": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "example": "6284f91e51cc73dad4255eb3"
                      },
                      "userData": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                          "_id": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "example": "6283dc5a60d07bddfa09e3a2"
                          },
                          "userName": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "example": "aa"
                          },
                          "userPhoto": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "example": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/42748910?v=4"
                          },
                          "email": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "example": "aa@mail.com"
                          }
                        }
                      },
                      "discussContent": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "example": "外面看起來就超冷…\n\n我決定回被窩繼續睡…>.<-33"
                      },
                      "discussPhoto": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "example": ""
                      },
                      "tag": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "example": "標籤"
                      },
                      "likes": {
                        "type": "number",
                        "example": 0
                      },
                      "comments": {
                        "type": "number",
                        "example": 0
                      },
                      "createAt": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "example": "2022-05-18T13:48:14.766Z"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              },
              "xml": {
                "name": "main"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "apiKeyAuth": []
          }
        ]
      },
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "posts (貼文)"
        ],
        "description": "  新增單筆貼文  <ul>  <li>取得 Token 至上方 Authorize 按鈕以格式 <code>Bearer ＜Token＞</code> 加入設定，swagger 文件中鎖頭上鎖表示登入，可使用登入權限。</li>  <li>新增貼文需先有 user.id 登入取得 Tokne</li>  <li>資料格式查看必填欄位，點按下方 Model 切換後，屬性欄位名稱的後方紅色的 <code>*</code></li>  <li>透過 user.id 向 posts 的屬性欄位 <code>userData</code> 關連。</li>  </ul>  ",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "body",
            "in": "body",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "discussContent": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "example": "外面看起來就超冷…\n 我決定回被窩繼續睡…>.<-"
                },
                "discussPhoto": {
                  "type": "string",
